            "title": "盤中速報 - 榮科(4989)大漲7.39%，報109元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)28日13:00股價上漲7.5元，報109.0元，漲幅7.39%，成交3,021張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為電解銅箔之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌5.14%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲7.19%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,901 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1,834 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-67 張</li> <li>融資增減：-2,927 張</li> <li>融券增減：-13 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6434923",
